{"title":"Zipp’s trail-smoothing 3ZERO MOTO single-wall wheelset is back with a totally redesigned hub","link":"https://www.bikeradar.com/news/zipp-3zero-moto-2021/","date":1617890405000,"content":"<img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/04/zipp-WH-3ZERO-MOTO-ca29e82.jpg?quality=45&#038;resize=620,413\" srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/04/zipp-WH-3ZERO-MOTO-ca29e82.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=2400,1598 2400w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/04/zipp-WH-3ZERO-MOTO-ca29e82.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1920,1278 1920w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/04/zipp-WH-3ZERO-MOTO-ca29e82.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1440,959 1440w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/04/zipp-WH-3ZERO-MOTO-ca29e82.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1200,799 1200w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/04/zipp-WH-3ZERO-MOTO-ca29e82.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=960,639 960w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/04/zipp-WH-3ZERO-MOTO-ca29e82.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=720,479 720w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/04/zipp-WH-3ZERO-MOTO-ca29e82.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=576,383 576w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/04/zipp-WH-3ZERO-MOTO-ca29e82.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=360,239 360w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/04/zipp-WH-3ZERO-MOTO-ca29e82.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=180,119 180w, \" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" class=\"wp-image-625409 alignnone size-landscape_thumbnail\" alt=\"Zipp WH 3Zero Moto wheelset\" title=\"Zipp WH 3Zero Moto wheelset\" />                                            <p>Zipp’s 3ZERO MOTO carbon <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/features/best-mountain-bike-wheels/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">mountain bike wheelset</a> claims to help smooth out rough terrain, limit rim-smashing impacts, reduce pinch punctures and increase cornering grip through its built-in rim compliance.</p>\n<p>A new second-generation hub also improves claimed durability and further opens the wheels up to the electric mountain bike market.</p>\n<p>The 3ZERO MOTO uses a single-wall construction. In this arrangement, there is only one layer of material, as opposed to the box-section structure of most rims (this is inspired by motocross wheels, hence the name)</p>\n<p>This setup is built to allow ‘local flex’ in the rim, as SRAM (Zipp’s parent company) puts it.</p>\n<div class=\"image-handler__container image-handler__container--full\" style=\"padding-bottom: calc(100% * (900 / 1352));\">\n    <picture><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/04/zipp-3zero-moto-mtb-02-1554454229807-45upaiq5ugpy-2a8f287-e1572522068904.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=300%2C200, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/04/zipp-3zero-moto-mtb-02-1554454229807-45upaiq5ugpy-2a8f287-e1572522068904.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=600%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/04/zipp-3zero-moto-mtb-02-1554454229807-45upaiq5ugpy-2a8f287-e1572522068904.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=900%2C599 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/04/zipp-3zero-moto-mtb-02-1554454229807-45upaiq5ugpy-2a8f287-e1572522068904.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1200%2C799 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/04/zipp-3zero-moto-mtb-02-1554454229807-45upaiq5ugpy-2a8f287-e1572522068904.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=300%2C200, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/04/zipp-3zero-moto-mtb-02-1554454229807-45upaiq5ugpy-2a8f287-e1572522068904.jpg?qualit