 type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/04/zipp-WH-3ZERO-MOTO-hubs-cutaway-2fd12bf.png?quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/04/zipp-WH-3ZERO-MOTO-hubs-cutaway-2fd12bf.png?quality=45&amp;resize=1110%2C740 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/04/zipp-WH-3ZERO-MOTO-hubs-cutaway-2fd12bf.png?quality=45&amp;resize=1667%2C1111 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/04/zipp-WH-3ZERO-MOTO-hubs-cutaway-2fd12bf.png?quality=45&amp;resize=2222%2C1481 4x\" type=\"image/png\"><img class=\"wp-image-625411 align size-landscape_thumbnail image-handler__image image-handler__image--aspect no-wrap js-lazyload\" data-src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/04/zipp-WH-3ZERO-MOTO-hubs-cutaway-2fd12bf.png?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Zipp WH 3Zero Moto wheelset hub\" title=\"Zipp WH 3Zero Moto wheelset hub\"></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></picture></div><div class=\"caption-hold\"><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span class=\"caption-copy\"><i class=\"icon-arrow icon-camera-circle\"></i> The hub has been totally redesigned.</span></figcaption><span class=\"im-image-caption\"> <i>Zipp</i></span></div>\n<p>While little has changed in the rim construction, the new ZM2 hub has been built to be more robust than its predecessor.</p>\n<p>There are now 12 pawls (four groups of three pawls) and 132 points of engagement, plus improved bearing seal design, according to SRAM.</p>\n<p>This means greater durability and faster engagement. A higher load transmission capability results in a hub and wheelset that is built for the rigours of ebike riding and the extra force it puts through components.</p>\n<div class=\"imag